	<doc for="InputLanguage.InstalledInputLanguages">
		<summary>
			<para> Gets a list of all installed input languages.
      </para>
		</summary>
		<value>
			<para> An array of <see cref="System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage"/> objects that represent the input
   languages installed on the computer.
   </para>
		</value>
		<example>
			<para> The following
      example retrieves all the input languages installed on
      the computer and displays their names. The code
      calls <see cref="System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage.InstalledInputLanguages"/>
      to get the installed languages. A
      text box displays the list of language names.
      </para>
			<para> This code assumes that <c>textBox1</c> has been instantiated and
   that <c>textBox1.MultiLine</c>
has been set to <see langword="true"/> .</para>
			<codelink SampleID="Classic InputLanguage.InstalledInputLanguages Example" SnippetID="1"/>
		</example>
